<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>ạlạ̉b fạdy jndḥ, sẖạrl sẖlạlạ</author>
<hymn_number>7055</hymn_number>
<title>ạ̉ntẓrk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉ntẓrk yạ rwḥ ạllh wmn gẖyrk ylyq bh ạlạ̹ntẓạr
 ạntẓạr ạlflạḥ llkẖryf
 ạntẓạr ạltrbh llsẖtạʾ
 ạntẓạr ạlbrʿm llrbyʿ
 ạntẓạr ạlḥṣạd llṣyf
 ạlqrạr- y̱tʿạl tʿạl tʿạl yạrwḥ ạllh
 2- yạ fạḥṣ ạʿmạqy hlm tʿạl
 kl mạ fy dẖạty yntẓr sẖfạỷk
 yạ ʿrys rwḥy hlm tʿạl
 kl mạ fy kyạny yntẓr ḥnạnk
 yạ wlymẗ jwʿy hlm tʿạl
 kl mạ fy qlby yntẓr slạmk
 yạʿmq bỷry hlm tʿạl
 kl mạ fy jwfy yntẓr sẖtạỷk</lyrics>
</song>